 string   `json:\"id\"`\n    41ŌåÆ\tProjectDir     string   `json:\"project_dir\"`\n    42ŌåÆ\tWorkflowName   string   `json:\"workflow_name\"`\n    43ŌåÆ\tTriggerRunID   string   `json:\"trigger_run_id\"`\n    44ŌåÆ\tTimestamp      string   `json:\"timestamp\"`\n    45ŌåÆ\tClassification string   `json:\"classification\"`\n    46ŌåÆ\tChanges        []Change `json:\"changes\"`\n    47ŌåÆ\tKnowledgeDelta string   `json:\"knowledge_delta\"`\n    48ŌåÆ}\n    49ŌåÆ\n    50ŌåÆ// Change describes a single file modification made by evolution.\n    51ŌåÆtype Change struct {\n    52ŌåÆ\tType     string `json:\"type\"`\n    53ŌåÆ\tFile     string `json:\"file\"`\n    54ŌåÆ\tReason   string `json:\"reason\"`\n    55ŌåÆ\tSnapshot string `json:\"snapshot\"`\n    56ŌåÆ}\n    57ŌåÆ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01LT97MYBGAi8gkxnHwbV9DE","session_id":"feb5bdf8-ca69-4cf3-a66e-11041ffe134a","uuid":"77635432-174a-4d53-96fa-c59320c4d80f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:12:23.309Z"}
